snippet.textDisplay:
But some questions: WHY the song durations are shorter and not much longer than this? Like khalsi is not even 5 mins song, even its arrangement and everything feels like the song ends before it gets to us. 6-7mins long average song is much better with detailex and patience in composition, the songs arrangement seems IN RUSH (its the same with this season's almost every songs). 
Want songs from elder artists too from various parts of Bharat❤ who treasures age old traditional music, folklores. We need to preserve them. And PLEASE MAKE SONGS FOR ALL GENERATIONS , not only youth, and with much beautiful melodies, sur, taal, indian classical inclusion both musically and instrumentally❤
